WRITING.TEXT: I think a "Make unique" button is very cool feature in FL to switch some parts of the beat fast.
this will allow you to create a unique copy of any pattern from your playlist and quickly edit it from piano roll so you don't have to create another pattern
just click that little arrow button on your pattern. [https://imgur.com/JjfelqH](https://imgur.com/JjfelqH) #8203; I'm using FL 12 btw

WRITING.TITLE: Juice WRLD Type Beat - Reliance [Prod. By SONIUS] 2019

WRITING.TEXT: If you look back like 3 years ago the sound of trap music was completely different from nowadays. It's a very young genre and it will keep changing, that's why it still on top imo

this is not very good because it makes your frequency range messy, it is much better to use leveling and select the necessary instruments to boost volume, the compressor can be used on kick or other drums, but not too much
